"Core" means the official proprietary Core plugin, its compiled bytecode,
license checks, private APIs, dashboard integration, premium automation logic,
and any feature identified by the Official Project as paid, premium, private,
or Core-only.

"Noncommercial Personal Use" means use by an individual for personal testing,
learning, private automation, or private modification, without revenue,
compensation, sponsorship, advertising, paid hosting, resale, consulting,
commercial advantage, or use on behalf of an organization.

"Fork" means a copy or derivative of the Software made for personal changes or
for proposing contributions back to the Official Project.

